00:04:42.380 --> 00:04:44.220
The system of taxation and types of

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:45.500
taxes and fees in Russia is

00:04:45.500 --> 00:04:47.100
established by the Constitution

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:49.700
of the Russian Federation and the Tax

00:04:49.700 --> 00:04:50.980
Code of Russia.

00:04:51.860 --> 00:04:53.620
Federal, regional and local

00:04:53.620 --> 00:04:55.960
taxes are currently established.

00:04:55.960 --> 00:04:57.360


00:04:57.420 --> 00:04:59.620
Federal taxes shall be established the

00:04:59.620 --> 00:05:02.060
same for all enterprises, organizations,

00:05:02.220 --> 00:05:04.940
individuals, existing, living

00:05:05.140 --> 00:05:06.800
and conducting their activities

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:08.980
in the territory of the

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:11.460
Russian Federation.

00:05:12.100 --> 00:05:13.260
Regional taxes are established

00:05:13.260 --> 00:05:14.960
by the subjects of the Russian Federation,

00:05:14.960 --> 00:05:16.760
respectively, and are obligatory

00:05:16.860 --> 00:05:18.800
for application on the territory

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:20.560
of these subjects.

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:22.700
Local taxes are established by

00:05:22.700 --> 00:05:25.040
local self-government bodies.

00:05:25.480 --> 00:05:29.100
There are currently nine

00:05:29.100 --> 00:05:31.120
types of federal taxes.

00:05:31.740 --> 00:05:33.680
These are known taxes, such

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:35.380
as value added tax,

00:05:35.380 --> 00:05:38.020
income tax, excise duties,

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:40.900
state duties, fees for the

00:05:41.260 --> 00:05:43.280
use of animal world objects

00:05:43.280 --> 00:05:46.780
and some other taxes.

00:05:46.780 --> 00:05:49.120
Regional taxes include the tax

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:51.080
on the property of legal entities,

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:54.900
the property tax of the local

00:05:54.900 --> 00:05:56.920
tax includes the land

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:58.720
tax and the property tax

00:05:58.720 --> 00:06:01.000
of natural persons.

00:06:01.300 --> 00:06:03.680
All of the above taxes have

00:06:03.680 --> 00:06:05.620
the same economic nature.

00:06:06.140 --> 00:06:08.060
As an economic category, any tax reflects

00:06:08.060 --> 00:06:09.960
the relationship between the state,

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:12.140
the population and the legal

00:06:12.140 --> 00:06:18.860
measures received by the population

00:06:18.860 --> 00:06:23.000
or legal entities for the purpose

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.320
of governmental needs.

00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:27.160
More specifically, the

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:29.640
tax can be considered as

00:06:29.660 --> 00:06:32.440
a free, mandatory payment

00:06:32.440 --> 00:06:34.740
required for

00:06:34.740 --> 00:06:37.640
the needs of the state

00:06:37.640 --> 00:06:39.060
budget or for non-budgetary

00:06:39.060 --> 00:06:41.120
state funds, such as

00:06:41.180 --> 00:06:49.360
the Pension Fund, the

00:06:49.360 --> 00:06:52.360
Medical Social Fund.

00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:54.360
The first and most important function

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:56.740
of taxation is fiscal.

00:06:57.340 --> 00:06:59.880
The essence of this function is

00:06:59.880 --> 00:07:04.280
that taxes should supplement the income

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:06.260
of the state treasury

00:07:06.260 --> 00:07:08.460
and extra-budgetary state funds.

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:11.080
Regulatory function also has a great

00:07:11.080 --> 00:07:14.660
importance supplementation and

00:07:14.660 --> 00:07:16.760
regulation of certain types of

00:07:16.760 --> 00:07:18.380
activities that are

00:07:18.380 --> 00:07:20.520
carried out in our country.

00:07:20.660 --> 00:07:22.280
Thus, individual types of taxes

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:23.900
by means of tax benefits allow

00:07:23.900 --> 00:07:29.800
to develop activities, for

00:07:29.800 --> 00:07:31.540
example, related to the creation

00:07:31.540 --> 00:07:36.620
of jobs for disabled people.

00:07:36.620 --> 00:07:42.540
Other taxes narrow activities,

00:07:42.540 --> 00:07:45.380
such as those related to the

00:07:45.380 --> 00:07:49.280
development of natural minerals.

00:07:49.680 --> 00:07:51.960
The third function that performs

00:07:51.960 --> 00:07:55.660
all taxes is the control function.

00:07:55.760 --> 00:07:57.840
The state, by means of taxes,

00:07:57.840 --> 00:07:58.580
controls the

00:07:58.580 --> 00:07:59.760
financial and economic

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:01.480
activities of enterprises or

00:08:01.480 --> 00:08:02.780
individuals.

00:08:03.100 --> 00:08:05.520
In addition to taxes, there are also fees in the

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:06.140
country.

00:08:06.140 --> 00:08:09.020
The fee is a mandatory payment

00:08:09.420 --> 00:08:13.240
that is mandatory when performing

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:14.800
certain legal actions,

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:17.260
when issuing rights or when

00:08:17.260 --> 00:08:20.340
issuing a license.

00:08:21.420 --> 00:08:24.900
In addition to taxes and fees, the concept of

00:08:24.900 --> 00:08:27.260
payments to the budget, such as fines and

00:08:27.260 --> 00:08:30.700
fines, is in place in the country.

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:34.900
Pennies are the amounts you are obliged

00:08:34.900 --> 00:08:37.580
to pay to the budget if you

00:08:37.580 --> 00:08:41.060
miss the period of payment of

00:08:41.060 --> 00:08:43.580
taxes and fees established by law.

00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:46.060
The taxation practice, which is

00:08:46.060 --> 00:08:48.920
applied in different countries,

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:51.060
has developed certain uniform

00:08:51.060 --> 00:08:53.580
principles for all taxation systems.

00:08:54.500 --> 00:08:55.900
One of the main principles

00:08:55.900 --> 00:08:59.260
is the proportionality of expenses

00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:03.940
in the form of taxes and income.

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:05.680
It is also called the

00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:08.880
principle of justice,

00:09:08.880 --> 00:09:10.960
when citizens and with

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:13.480
higher incomes

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:15.880
pay higher taxes.

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:18.200
For example, in Russia last

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.420
year was submitted

00:09:19.420 --> 00:09:26.240
to the State B list of luxury

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:28.360
items subject to this

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:30.600
tax, including apartments

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:33.720
worth more than 15

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:35.720
million rubles, cars, aircraft,

00:09:35.720 --> 00:09:38.680
boats worth more than

00:09:39.380 --> 00:09:41.220
2 million rubles and

00:09:41.220 --> 00:09:43.740
jewelry, as well as

00:09:43.740 --> 00:09:45.720
art objects worth more

00:09:45.940 --> 00:09:48.440
than 300 thousand

00:09:48.440 --> 00:09:49.360
rubles.

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:52.360
The next principle of the organization

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:55.040
of the tax system is the principle

00:09:55.040 --> 00:09:57.960
of conformity of the payment of

00:09:57.960 --> 00:10:00.720
tax to the income received.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.040
This means that the tax cannot be

00:10:02.040 --> 00:10:04.940
paid on previously received income.

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:06.840
Another principle of the organization

00:10:06.840 --> 00:10:09.580
of the taxation system is the clarity

00:10:09.580 --> 00:10:13.520
of the formulations and principles

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:16.360
of the amount of the time period

00:10:16.360 --> 00:10:18.060
for establishing the tax, which

00:10:18.060 --> 00:10:23.140
must be set out in certain

00:10:23.140 --> 00:10:25.100
formulations in the legislation,

00:10:25.340 --> 00:10:28.340
which can be accessible to all citizens.

00:10:28.420 --> 00:10:32.580
With all the uniformity of taxes for

00:10:32.580 --> 00:10:35.060
all enterprises and organizations

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:36.560
operating in the territory of a country,

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:40.160
the result in the form of taxes

