The tax amnesty provides for the amnesty

00:22:35.530 --> 00:22:38.390
of the amounts of income

00:22:38.470 --> 00:22:40.410
that were received by individuals

00:22:40.410 --> 00:22:43.290
before 2006.

00:22:44.070 --> 00:22:45.550
I would like to point out

00:22:45.550 --> 00:22:47.330
that tax amnesty, wherever

00:22:47.330 --> 00:22:50.530
it is, is for individuals

00:22:50.530 --> 00:22:53.930
and not for legal entities.

00:22:53.930 --> 00:22:56.590
If a legal entity has violated

00:22:56.590 --> 00:22:58.530
the rules for calculating certain

00:22:58.530 --> 00:23:00.230
taxes and fees, certain

00:23:00.230 --> 00:23:03.110
measures are provided

00:23:03.110 --> 00:23:06.710
for for this, but not tax amnesty.

00:23:06.930 --> 00:23:09.270
The last tax amnesty was successfully

00:23:09.270 --> 00:23:13.010
held last year, the nearest has

00:23:13.470 --> 00:23:16.070
not yet been identified.

00:23:16.430 --> 00:23:18.730
In order to conduct such effective

00:23:18.730 --> 00:23:22.830
tax naturally, our tax service

00:23:23.110 --> 00:23:24.930
requests advice from other

00:23:24.930 --> 00:23:28.470
