00:23:36.430 --> 00:23:38.650
was used for tax amnesty,

00:23:38.650 --> 00:23:42.570
where the majority of amnesty

00:23:42.570 --> 00:23:45.450
amounts were received in

00:23:45.450 --> 00:23:49.210
the last days of amnesty.

