00:27:35.510 --> 00:27:37.410
Let us consider the procedure for

00:27:37.410 --> 00:27:39.550
calculating taxes and fees,

00:27:39.550 --> 00:27:42.450
which is in effect in Russia in more detail.

00:27:42.910 --> 00:27:44.890
With all the diversity of taxes

00:27:44.890 --> 00:27:46.550
and fees, there is a certain

00:27:46.550 --> 00:27:48.110
general rule that applies

00:27:48.170 --> 00:27:51.590
to all types of taxes and fees.

00:27:54.310 --> 00:27:56.010
These are some elements that are

00:27:56.010 --> 00:28:01.090
mandatory for the beginning

00:28:01.090 --> 00:28:02.470
of certain taxes.

00:28:03.150 --> 00:28:04.930
For example, a tax object,

00:28:04.930 --> 00:28:08.030
which is established

00:28:08.030 --> 00:28:09.930
literally for all taxes, the only

00:28:09.930 --> 00:28:12.370
difference can be the nature

00:28:12.370 --> 00:28:16.270
of the object itself.

00:28:16.270 --> 00:28:18.210
For example, it can be the volume

00:28:18.210 --> 00:28:20.710
of sales of goods, works, services,

00:28:20.990 --> 00:28:24.490
income, property or other circumstance,

00:28:24.490 --> 00:28:26.130
when the occurrence of which

00:28:26.170 --> 00:28:32.150
is considered to be a tax.

00:28:32.570 --> 00:28:35.270
Tax bases are a timestone physical

00:28:35.270 --> 00:28:37.390
or other characteristic of the

00:28:37.390 --> 00:28:39.050
object of taxation.

00:28:39.490 --> 00:28:41.110
The tax bases for different

00:28:41.110 --> 00:28:44.250
taxes can be very different.

00:28:44.250 --> 00:28:49.210
In this case, some special conditions for

00:28:49.210 --> 00:28:53.870
implementation of a particular implementation

00:28:53.870 --> 00:28:56.350
are taken into account.

00:28:56.770 --> 00:28:59.350
For example, the tax base

00:28:59.350 --> 00:29:02.290
for the sale of services to so-

00:29:02.290 --> 00:29:04.530
called interdependent persons

00:29:04.530 --> 00:29:07.350
is calculated in a special way.

00:29:07.650 --> 00:29:08.690
A small example.

00:29:08.690 --> 00:29:13.670
If you have sold your products

00:29:13.670 --> 00:29:16.110
to a mutually dependent entity,

00:29:16.110 --> 00:29:17.830
i.e. a legal entity that

00:29:17.830 --> 00:29:22.870
participates in your capital

00:29:22.870 --> 00:29:26.890
within 20%, or a person who

00:29:26.890 --> 00:29:34.670
is with you in a specified position

00:29:34.670 --> 00:29:36.890
or relative, no matter

00:29:36.890 --> 00:29:38.670
brother, sister, wife or

00:29:38.770 --> 00:29:40.590
husband, then the tax

00:29:40.590 --> 00:29:42.290
base can be converted

00:29:42.290 --> 00:29:45.650
at market prices.

00:29:45.990 --> 00:29:48.210
These rules of special calculation

00:29:48.210 --> 00:29:51.890
of the tax base can be considered, with

00:29:52.230 --> 00:29:54.130
them you can get acquainted in Article

00:29:54.130 --> 00:29:57.230
40 of Part 1 of the Tax Code.

