is the procedure for payment of

00:30:06.290 --> 00:30:07.930
taxes and fees.

00:30:08.390 --> 00:30:12.270
The payment procedure may be different

00:30:12.270 --> 00:30:17.610
as the reporting period occurs,

00:30:17.610 --> 00:30:20.030
for example, a quarter or a month,

00:30:20.030 --> 00:30:25.870
after the expiry of the tax

00:30:25.870 --> 00:30:28.870
rate on different taxes can be established

00:30:28.870 --> 00:30:30.390
in both a solid amount

00:30:30.390 --> 00:30:31.990
and a percentage of the

00:30:31.990 --> 00:30:34.310
tax base.

