the rate is 0%, when selling

00:30:53.110 --> 00:30:55.030
food or medical goods

00:30:55.030 --> 00:30:56.350
the tax rate is

00:30:56.350 --> 00:30:59.770
10%, when selling

00:30:59.770 --> 00:31:01.390
other goods the

00:31:01.390 --> 00:31:05.410
maximum is 18%.

00:31:05.410 --> 00:31:07.550
The tax rate can be in

00:31:07.550 --> 00:31:10.910
rubles or in percentage.

00:31:11.390 --> 00:31:12.990
The income tax rate is

00:31:12.990 --> 00:31:16.110
also in percentage.

00:31:17.550 --> 00:31:22.170
The tax procedure and time limits

00:31:22.170 --> 00:31:24.170
may also be different.

00:31:25.490 --> 00:31:26.790
For example, the value added tax

00:31:26.790 --> 00:31:32.390
must be paid no later than the

00:31:32.390 --> 00:31:36.170
20th of the month following the

00:31:36.170 --> 00:31:37.810
reporting quarter.

00:31:37.810 --> 00:31:40.630
It will be no later than April 20,

00:31:40.630 --> 00:31:45.930
July 20, October 20 and January 20.

00:31:47.070 --> 00:31:48.790
The income tax shall be paid no

00:31:48.790 --> 00:31:52.850
later than 28 of the day,

00:31:52.850 --> 00:31:55.350
which was listed when considering

00:31:55.350 --> 00:31:57.930
the payment of value added tax.

00:31:59.010 --> 00:32:00.570
The single tax in the simplified

00:32:00.570 --> 00:32:01.870
taxation system shall be

00:32:01.870 --> 00:32:03.890
paid no later than the 25th of the

00:32:03.930 --> 00:32:06.110
month following the reporting period.

00:32:06.790 --> 00:32:08.510
Some enterprises or some

00:32:08.510 --> 00:32:12.410
taxpayers may be provided with

00:32:12.410 --> 00:32:14.890
tax benefits for payment

00:32:14.890 --> 00:32:17.350
of certain taxes and fees.

00:32:17.670 --> 00:32:20.510
They are provided in different variants.

00:32:20.530 --> 00:32:23.630
For example, a certain minimum

00:32:23.630 --> 00:32:25.830
of the accrued tax may not be

00:32:25.830 --> 00:32:27.850
taxable, for example, the minimum

00:32:27.850 --> 00:32:29.750
wage is not taxed.

00:32:30.810 --> 00:32:32.110
Tax benefits may be granted

00:32:40.250 --> 00:32:41.970
to non-taxable property transferred

00:32:41.970 --> 00:32:44.330
by the founder of the organization

00:32:44.370 --> 00:32:47.310
in favour of this organization

00:32:47.310 --> 00:32:49.930
during the year, if

00:32:49.930 --> 00:32:52.670
this property was not

00:32:52.670 --> 00:32:56.770
sold to other persons.

00:32:57.950 --> 00:33:01.910
Tax benefits are established by

00:33:01.910 --> 00:33:03.190
some category of taxpayers,

00:33:03.190 --> 00:33:06.150
for example, disabled persons.

00:33:06.710 --> 00:33:10.130
The taxes and fees are calculated

00:33:10.130 --> 00:33:14.850
independently and submitted

00:33:14.850 --> 00:33:16.910
to the tax inspectorate

00:33:16.910 --> 00:33:20.050
in the form of a tax declaration.

00:33:20.410 --> 00:33:22.090
The tax declaration may be submitted

00:33:22.090 --> 00:33:24.350
by the tax inspector personally by the

00:33:24.350 --> 00:33:26.850
chief accountant or the head of the

00:33:26.850 --> 00:33:29.190
enterprise, may be transmitted by mail

00:33:29.510 --> 00:33:32.010
with an inventory of the investment

00:33:32.010 --> 00:33:35.750
or transmitted on the Internet.

00:33:35.850 --> 00:33:38.490
In any case, this is not specified

00:33:38.490 --> 00:33:40.550
and at any time the order of

00:33:40.550 --> 00:33:42.550
submission of the tax declaration

00:33:42.550 --> 00:33:44.030
may be different.

00:33:44.150 --> 00:33:46.910
In addition to taxes, there is a

00:33:46.910 --> 00:33:49.450
duty of taxpayers to calculate

00:33:49.450 --> 00:33:51.410
and pay advance payments

00:33:51.410 --> 00:33:53.110
on certain taxes and fees within

00:33:53.110 --> 00:33:55.770
the established time limits.

00:33:55.890 --> 00:33:58.850
Advance payments are

00:33:58.850 --> 00:34:01.270
equal to the same equivalent

00:34:01.270 --> 00:34:05.190
taxes and fees.

00:34:05.350 --> 00:34:07.170
Advance payments are provided for the

00:34:07.170 --> 00:34:08.250
following taxes.

00:34:08.250 --> 00:34:11.470
Profit tax, land tax, transport

00:34:11.590 --> 00:34:14.530
tax, property tax.

00:34:15.770 --> 00:34:19.410
The obligation is considered fulfilled

00:34:21.070 --> 00:34:25.050
when the payment order with the amount

00:34:25.050 --> 00:34:28.070
of tax is transferred to the bank in the

00:34:28.070 --> 00:34:29.810
presence of the corresponding balance

00:34:29.810 --> 00:34:32.250
of funds in the enterprise.

00:34:32.370 --> 00:34:35.150
In addition, the duty to pay taxes

00:34:35.150 --> 00:34:36.490
is considered to be fully fulfilled

00:34:36.490 --> 00:34:39.770
when the company is liquidated.

00:34:39.870 --> 00:34:41.410
Of course, all the budget

00:34:41.410 --> 00:34:43.370
calculations must be completed.

00:34:44.310 --> 00:34:46.050
Now we will consider in more

00:34:46.050 --> 00:34:49.550
detail the procedure for calculating

00:34:49.550 --> 00:34:51.510
some of the taxes and fees

00:34:51.510 --> 00:34:53.690
most common in the Russian

00:34:54.750 --> 00:34:56.550
Federation.

00:34:56.990 --> 00:35:01.390
Let us start with the value added tax.

00:35:01.850 --> 00:35:04.310
Value added tax is a tax calculated

00:35:04.310 --> 00:35:06.730
from the value of the

00:35:06.730 --> 00:35:10.910
products produced, performed

00:35:10.910 --> 00:35:13.450
works or rendered services.

00:35:13.450 --> 00:35:14.710


00:35:14.950 --> 00:35:19.070
It was introduced in Russia in 1992

00:35:19.070 --> 00:35:21.410
and is currently regulated by 21

00:35:21.410 --> 00:35:23.730
chapters of the Tax Code.

00:35:24.010 --> 00:35:26.190
Taxpayers of this tax are all enterprises,

00:35:26.190 --> 00:35:29.590
legal entities of the Russian

00:35:29.690 --> 00:35:33.090
Federation, as well as foreign

00:35:33.090 --> 00:35:36.210
organizations of enterprises that

00:35:36.210 --> 00:35:38.130
carry out activities in the territory

00:35:38.130 --> 00:35:39.670
of the Russian Federation

00:35:39.670 --> 00:35:42.670
or import goods into

00:35:42.670 --> 00:35:45.730
the customs territory of

00:35:45.730 --> 00:35:47.410
the Russian Federation.

00:35:49.750 --> 00:35:51.750
Any enterprises may be exempt

00:35:51.750 --> 00:35:53.730
from payment of this tax

00:35:53.730 --> 00:35:55.310
when fulfilling certain

00:35:55.310 --> 00:35:57.450
conditions provided

00:35:57.510 --> 00:35:59.770
for by Chapter 21 of the

00:35:59.770 --> 00:36:01.430
Tax Code and when providing

00:36:01.430 --> 00:36:03.370
the relevant package of

00:36:03.370 --> 00:36:04.710
documents.

00:36:05.290 --> 00:36:07.550
The exemption can be obtained no later

00:36:07.550 --> 00:36:10.370
than the 20th day, when the relevant

00:36:10.370 --> 00:36:13.330
notification has been submitted to the

00:36:13.330 --> 00:36:14.790
tax authorities.

00:36:15.150 --> 00:36:18.010
At the same time, it should be borne in

00:36:18.010 --> 00:36:19.290
mind that an enterprise which

00:36:19.290 --> 00:36:21.390
has received an exemption, which is in

00:36:21.390 --> 00:36:24.610
effect within 12 months after the

00:36:24.610 --> 00:36:26.690
submission of the relevant application,

00:36:26.690 --> 00:36:29.610
is not exempt from issuing invoices

00:36:29.610 --> 00:36:31.490
for the goods produced

00:36:31.490 --> 00:36:35.310
by the enterprise, services rendered

00:36:35.310 --> 00:36:37.270
or works performed.

00:36:37.270 --> 00:36:41.750
The VAT amount in the invoice is indicated

00:36:41.750 --> 00:36:44.910
at zero rate, that is, it is

00:36:44.910 --> 00:36:47.350
not available at all.

00:36:47.590 --> 00:36:50.790
Enterprises must submit tax declarations

00:36:50.790 --> 00:36:52.870
with scripts within the same

00:36:52.870 --> 00:36:55.370
time limits as those established

00:36:55.370 --> 00:36:59.110
for ordinary enterprises

00:36:59.110 --> 00:37:01.790
who are VAT payers.

00:37:02.930 --> 00:37:04.950
The subject of taxation on

00:37:04.950 --> 00:37:08.050
value added tax are the following

00:37:08.050 --> 00:37:14.650
types of implementation.

00:37:15.250 --> 00:37:18.210
These are goods, works, services

00:37:18.350 --> 00:37:20.190
that have been produced at your

00:37:20.190 --> 00:37:23.130
enterprise or goods that have

00:37:23.130 --> 00:37:25.210
been purchased for resale.

00:37:25.330 --> 00:37:28.090
For example, you bought a product for 100

00:37:28.090 --> 00:37:31.130
rubles, sold it for 120, the object of

00:37:31.130 --> 00:37:34.690
taxation will be the difference.

00:37:35.310 --> 00:37:38.190
The tax will be charged to the total

00:37:38.190 --> 00:37:39.850
amount of goods sold, i.e.

00:37:39.850 --> 00:37:41.090
120 rubles.

00:37:42.130 --> 00:37:44.030
In the case of the transfer of

00:37:44.030 --> 00:37:46.990
property, work, services, the subject

00:37:46.990 --> 00:37:48.970
of taxation shall be considered the

00:37:48.970 --> 00:37:53.190
market price of these works, services

00:37:53.190 --> 00:37:54.370
or property.

00:37:54.830 --> 00:37:58.010
A small example, for example,

00:37:58.010 --> 00:38:00.930
you move from one to another and

00:38:00.930 --> 00:38:05.930
left the furniture to the tenant

00:38:05.930 --> 00:38:09.950
or future tenant of that room.

00:38:10.790 --> 00:38:12.330
The residual value

00:38:12.330 --> 00:38:15.030
of this property will be

00:38:15.030 --> 00:38:17.590
the object of taxation

00:38:17.590 --> 00:38:18.910
on value added.

00:38:19.630 --> 00:38:21.490
Construction works for

00:38:21.490 --> 00:38:23.050
own consumption

00:38:23.050 --> 00:38:24.570
are also subject

00:38:24.570 --> 00:38:27.570
to taxation.

00:38:28.010 --> 00:38:31.570
For example, an organization performing

00:38:31.570 --> 00:38:33.790
construction, installation, repair

00:38:33.790 --> 00:38:36.470
work in the country has built

00:38:36.470 --> 00:38:39.050
a pool for its own consumption,

00:38:39.050 --> 00:38:40.590
that is, for use by

00:38:40.590 --> 00:38:43.410
employees of the enterprise.

00:38:43.590 --> 00:38:45.250
The cost of the pool will

00:38:45.250 --> 00:38:47.910
also be subject to taxation.

00:38:48.550 --> 00:38:52.790
If you have imported goods into the territory

00:38:52.790 --> 00:38:55.430
of the Russian Federation

00:38:55.550 --> 00:38:58.790
from abroad, the value of goods determined

00:38:58.790 --> 00:39:00.390
by the Customs Code of the Russian

00:39:00.390 --> 00:39:02.810
Federation will also be subject

00:39:02.810 --> 00:39:04.470
to taxation.

00:39:05.090 --> 00:39:07.210
The time limit for payment of value

00:39:07.210 --> 00:39:10.690
added tax is the 20th of the month

00:39:10.690 --> 00:39:12.830
following the reporting quarter.

00:39:13.070 --> 00:39:21.270
Reporting period since 2008 for taxation.

00:39:21.550 --> 00:39:27.070
The main rates are 0.10 and 18%.

00:39:27.070 --> 00:39:30.070
The tax base is calculated as the difference

00:39:30.070 --> 00:39:32.330
between the amount of goods

00:39:32.330 --> 00:39:34.930
sold and the amount of services and

00:39:34.930 --> 00:39:37.710
tax deductions or the year established

00:39:37.810 --> 00:39:41.330
by Chapter 21 of the Tax Code.

00:39:42.070 --> 00:39:44.010
The slide is an example of calculation of the

00:39:44.010 --> 00:39:45.490
amount of the tax on the added Example of

00:39:45.750 --> 00:39:49.190
calculation of the amount of VAT.

