The company purchased materials for the

00:39:51.970 --> 00:39:54.810
amount of 59 thousand rubles, including

00:39:54.810 --> 00:39:57.390
the amount of VAT on the invoice

00:39:57.390 --> 00:40:00.950
submitted to you from the supplier was 9

00:40:00.950 --> 00:40:02.010
thousand rubles.

