In the same period, our company

00:40:04.470 --> 00:40:08.130
provided VAT-taxable services at

00:40:08.130 --> 00:40:11.010
the rate of 18 percent for the

00:40:11.010 --> 00:40:13.770
amount of 141,600 rubles, including

00:40:13.810 --> 00:40:16.230
VAT, which must be indicated

00:40:16.230 --> 00:40:19.410
in the invoice you issue, will

