2008, will be 12 600 rubles.

00:41:02.370 --> 00:41:04.070
Let us go to the common

00:41:04.070 --> 00:41:05.290
social tax.

00:41:05.390 --> 00:41:06.990
The unified social tax is

00:41:06.990 --> 00:41:09.050
intended for the mobilization of

00:41:09.190 --> 00:41:12.050
funds providing state pension

00:41:12.050 --> 00:41:14.170
and medical insurance of citizens

00:41:14.170 --> 00:41:18.470
of the Russian Federation.

00:41:21.250 --> 00:41:23.650
The procedure for taxation of

00:41:23.650 --> 00:41:26.610
this tax is considered in Chapter 24

00:41:26.610 --> 00:41:28.070
of the Tax Code.

00:41:28.450 --> 00:41:30.230
Who is the taxpayer of the

00:41:30.230 --> 00:41:31.990
single social tax?

00:41:32.070 --> 00:41:36.090
These include all enterprises,

00:41:36.150 --> 00:41:38.750
eridic persons, individual

00:41:39.110 --> 00:41:42.250
entrepreneurs, as well as lawyers

00:41:42.270 --> 00:41:47.090
who are not employers,

00:41:47.310 --> 00:41:53.030
who pay out collective

00:41:54.570 --> 00:41:58.030
labour contracts to individuals.

00:41:58.030 --> 00:42:00.190


00:42:00.750 --> 00:42:02.590
In the calculation of the single

00:42:02.590 --> 00:42:09.190
social tax progressive tax rates.

00:42:09.850 --> 00:42:14.090
The higher the taxpayer's income,

00:42:14.710 --> 00:42:17.530
the lower the rate of the

00:42:17.530 --> 00:42:19.350
single social tax.

00:42:19.350 --> 00:42:20.910
The maximum rate of the single

00:42:20.910 --> 00:42:22.270
social tax for today is 12% of

00:42:22.270 --> 00:42:25.970
the amounts of payments, and to the

00:42:25.970 --> 00:42:29.210
pension fund 14%.

00:42:29.210 --> 00:42:31.690
The subject of taxation of the

00:42:31.690 --> 00:42:35.010
single social tax is the payments

00:42:35.010 --> 00:42:37.050
of the employer in favor of

00:42:37.050 --> 00:42:38.950
employees, calculated firstly on

00:42:38.950 --> 00:42:40.630
labor contracts in accordance

00:42:40.630 --> 00:42:42.650
with the Labor Code, and secondly

00:42:42.690 --> 00:42:46.370
on civil law contracts.

00:42:48.650 --> 00:42:50.410
When paying the single social tax,

00:42:50.410 --> 00:42:52.890
a system of calculation and payment

00:42:52.890 --> 00:42:56.730
of advance payments is provided.

00:42:56.810 --> 00:42:58.310
Advance payments of the single

00:42:58.310 --> 00:43:00.710
social tax are calculated monthly

00:43:00.910 --> 00:43:04.730
until the 15th of the month following

00:43:04.730 --> 00:43:08.630
the reporting period.

00:43:09.030 --> 00:43:13.210
As a result, future advance

00:43:13.210 --> 00:43:16.230
payments take into account

00:43:16.230 --> 00:43:18.510
the amount of advance payments

00:43:18.510 --> 00:43:20.230
paid before.

00:43:20.270 --> 00:43:21.930
Consider a small example of calculation

00:43:21.930 --> 00:43:26.590
of the ESS and the amount of deductions

00:43:26.590 --> 00:43:27.930
to the Pension Fund of the Russian

00:43:27.930 --> 00:43:31.990
Federation on payments made by the employer

00:43:31.990 --> 00:43:34.430
in favor of the employee of the firm

00:43:34.430 --> 00:43:37.150
in accordance with the employment contract.

00:43:38.010 --> 00:43:41.250
In January 2008, the employee

00:43:41.250 --> 00:43:43.070
was charged 50 thousand

00:43:43.070 --> 00:43:44.370
rubles.

00:43:45.810 --> 00:43:48.410
The employer must calculate the amount

00:43:48.410 --> 00:43:50.930
of the single social tax and the amount

00:43:50.930 --> 00:43:52.510
of deductions to the Pension Fund of the

00:43:52.510 --> 00:43:55.270
Russian Federation accordingly,

00:43:55.270 --> 00:44:00.310
at rates of 12% SN and 14% pension fund.

00:44:00.550 --> 00:44:02.590
As a result, the employer's expenses

00:44:02.590 --> 00:44:04.770
for January 2008 on the

00:44:04.770 --> 00:44:06.970
charges made to this employee

00:44:06.970 --> 00:44:10.450
will be 13 thousand rubles.

00:44:11.690 --> 00:44:14.090
There are also tax benefits

00:44:14.090 --> 00:44:17.310
for this tax, which can be read

00:44:17.310 --> 00:44:21.730
in detail in Chapter 24 of

00:44:21.730 --> 00:44:22.770
the Tax Code.

00:44:22.770 --> 00:44:24.630
For example, benefits are

00:44:24.630 --> 00:44:28.730
provided for payments to disabled

00:44:28.730 --> 00:44:33.310
persons of groups 1, 2 and 3 within

00:44:33.310 --> 00:44:35.590
100 thousand rubles for the reporting

00:44:35.590 --> 00:44:36.950
period.

00:44:37.130 --> 00:44:38.930
Now to the next tax.

00:44:38.970 --> 00:44:40.430
Tax on Profit.

00:44:40.430 --> 00:44:41.950
The income tax, also called

00:44:41.950 --> 00:44:43.390
income tax, was introduced

00:44:43.390 --> 00:44:47.270
in our country for a long time,

00:44:47.270 --> 00:44:53.830
but the tax tax was introduced

00:44:53.830 --> 00:44:56.270
only in 2002.

00:44:56.690 --> 00:44:58.530
An entity can receive both

00:44:58.530 --> 00:45:01.270
profit and loss during a reporting

00:45:01.270 --> 00:45:04.230
or tax period, but income

00:45:04.710 --> 00:45:06.630
tax is naturally paid only

00:45:06.850 --> 00:45:09.170
on the received profit.

00:45:09.970 --> 00:45:11.770
Who is the taxpayer of

00:45:11.770 --> 00:45:13.190
this tax?

00:45:13.310 --> 00:45:14.890
Taxpayers of income tax carrying

00:45:22.170 --> 00:45:23.930
out their activities in the

00:45:23.930 --> 00:45:25.050
territory of the Russian Federation

00:45:25.050 --> 00:45:27.610
through a permanent representative

00:45:27.610 --> 00:45:30.410
office or receiving income

00:45:30.410 --> 00:45:35.430
from a Russian organization.

00:45:36.450 --> 00:45:38.230
The income tax is calculated at a

00:45:38.230 --> 00:45:41.630
rate of 24% from the general tax base.

00:45:41.670 --> 00:45:43.490
Also, for certain types of income,

00:45:43.490 --> 00:45:47.090
rates are provided in a smaller amount.

00:45:47.090 --> 00:45:50.970
For example, a 9% tax rate is provided

00:45:50.970 --> 00:45:53.470
in the form of dividends received

00:45:53.470 --> 00:45:56.710
by a Russian organization.

00:45:56.890 --> 00:46:00.890
The rate of 15% is provided for

00:46:00.890 --> 00:46:03.090
taxes in the form of dividends

00:46:03.090 --> 00:46:04.610
received by a foreign organization

00:46:04.610 --> 00:46:08.730
from a Russian organization.

00:46:08.730 --> 00:46:09.000


00:46:09.000 --> 00:46:09.750


00:46:09.750 --> 00:46:13.790
The income tax is calculated as the monetary

00:46:13.790 --> 00:46:16.050
expression of the profit received

00:46:16.070 --> 00:46:21.810
between the difference in income

00:46:21.810 --> 00:46:24.570
and expenses made in the reporting

00:46:24.570 --> 00:46:25.770
period.

