of a single tax on the assigned income

01:17:53.060 --> 01:17:55.500
is not optional.

01:17:55.740 --> 01:17:58.240
It is mandatory for all and

01:17:58.240 --> 01:18:00.100
entrepreneurs who carry

01:18:00.100 --> 01:18:02.600
out certain types of activities.

01:18:02.600 --> 01:18:04.760
Such activities include retail

01:18:04.760 --> 01:18:07.940
trade through bins, tents, kiosks

01:18:07.940 --> 01:18:11.020
that do not have their own shopping

01:18:11.020 --> 01:18:13.740
areas, car freight transportation,

01:18:17.800 --> 01:18:20.160
as well as passenger transportation,

01:18:20.160 --> 01:18:23.060
by those enterprises in which

01:18:23.060 --> 01:18:25.700
the number of cars

01:18:25.700 --> 01:18:27.460
does not exceed

01:18:27.460 --> 01:18:31.140
20 units.

01:18:33.240 --> 01:18:36.680
Car service services, household

01:18:36.680 --> 01:18:39.080
services are also subject

01:18:39.080 --> 01:18:41.480
to a single tax on income,

01:18:41.480 --> 01:18:47.300
but also some other more

01:18:47.300 --> 01:18:48.220
rare activities,

01:18:52.720 --> 01:18:58.120
you Tax Code.

01:18:58.260 --> 01:19:01.860
The object of taxation of the single

01:19:01.860 --> 01:19:03.960
tax system on the assigned income

01:19:03.960 --> 01:19:06.120
is the assigned income,

01:19:06.120 --> 01:19:07.940
determined for each type

01:19:07.940 --> 01:19:09.580
of activity separately.

01:19:10.920 --> 01:19:13.680
It should be noted that an enterprise

01:19:13.680 --> 01:19:16.960
may be simultaneously a payer

01:19:16.960 --> 01:19:18.820
of the single tax on the imposed

01:19:18.820 --> 01:19:20.340
income if it, for example,

01:19:20.340 --> 01:19:22.160
carries out cargo transportation

01:19:22.160 --> 01:19:25.020
and the amount of motor

01:19:25.160 --> 01:19:27.500
vehicles on the balance sheet

01:19:27.500 --> 01:19:29.920
or rented by this enterprise

01:19:29.920 --> 01:19:33.000
less than 20 units, less

01:19:33.080 --> 01:19:35.720
than 20 vehicles, it may also

01:19:35.720 --> 01:19:38.160
be a payer of basic taxes

01:19:38.640 --> 01:19:41.100
if it carries out

01:19:41.100 --> 01:19:43.180
other types of activities.

01:19:44.100 --> 01:19:45.400
I will give a small example.

01:19:45.580 --> 01:19:49.040
The company produces furniture,

01:19:49.040 --> 01:19:50.540
has its own production, its

01:19:50.800 --> 01:19:51.820
own building.

01:19:51.820 --> 01:19:55.180
The number of units of motor vehicles

01:19:55.180 --> 01:19:57.860
carried on its own vehicles

01:19:57.860 --> 01:20:00.200
up to 20 for example 15 cars, so

01:20:00.200 --> 01:20:04.160
the amounts received for the

01:20:04.160 --> 01:20:09.160
sale of furniture must be reflected

01:20:09.160 --> 01:20:12.120
by the general system of taxation,

01:20:12.120 --> 01:20:14.580
that is, this enterprise

01:20:14.580 --> 01:20:17.480
will pay VAT, will pay income

01:20:17.480 --> 01:20:19.880
tax, a single social tax on payments

01:20:20.660 --> 01:20:22.740
to employees of this furniture enterprise

01:20:23.000 --> 01:20:24.680
and at the same time on the activities

01:20:24.680 --> 01:20:26.420
related to the transportation

01:20:26.420 --> 01:20:29.100
of finished products in

01:20:29.100 --> 01:20:30.520
the form of furniture

01:20:30.520 --> 01:20:32.580
to buyers, will be taxed by

01:20:32.580 --> 01:20:35.020
the rates of the single

01:20:35.020 --> 01:20:39.420
tax on the tax on the

01:20:39.420 --> 01:20:41.600
taxable income, if this

01:20:41.600 --> 01:20:45.040
tax is legally introduced

01:20:45.040 --> 01:20:48.340
in this region.

01:20:49.380 --> 01:20:54.140
The rate is currently 15%.

01:20:55.620 --> 01:20:59.020
This rate is imposed on the income

01:20:59.020 --> 01:21:01.260
that has been established for

01:21:01.260 --> 01:21:03.500
this particular type of activity.

01:21:04.020 --> 01:21:09.740
The tax base in any reporting

01:21:09.740 --> 01:21:13.220
period does not depend on the

01:21:13.220 --> 01:21:15.520
income actually received.

01:21:15.520 --> 01:21:17.220
It depends on the physical

01:21:17.220 --> 01:21:19.020
indicator for the specific

01:21:19.020 --> 01:21:21.080
type of activity and the

01:21:21.080 --> 01:21:24.400
basic return established by law.

01:21:24.820 --> 01:21:26.020
The physical indicator

01:21:26.020 --> 01:21:27.580
is set specifically for each

01:21:27.580 --> 01:21:29.180
type of activity, for

01:21:29.960 --> 01:21:32.020
example, for retail, it will

01:21:32.020 --> 01:21:37.280
be the area on which

01:21:37.280 --> 01:21:38.540
sales are made.

01:21:39.120 --> 01:21:40.660
For retail trade, this area

01:21:40.660 --> 01:21:43.100
must be at least 150 square

01:21:43.100 --> 01:21:45.160
meters.

01:21:46.360 --> 01:21:50.260
At this area, a single tax on

01:21:50.260 --> 01:21:51.720
the income is calculated.

01:21:51.760 --> 01:21:53.660
If the area exceeds 150 square

01:21:53.660 --> 01:21:55.540
meters, then the general

01:21:55.540 --> 01:21:57.840
tax system is applied.

01:21:58.260 --> 01:21:59.920
The physical indicator for

01:21:59.920 --> 01:22:03.260
the activity on freight transportation

01:22:03.260 --> 01:22:08.840
will be the number of vehicles.

01:22:09.420 --> 01:22:12.080
The physical indicator for

01:22:12.080 --> 01:22:14.140
passenger transportation will

01:22:14.140 --> 01:22:16.640
be the number of passenger seats.

01:22:17.380 --> 01:22:21.240
Since 2008, such activities as land

01:22:21.240 --> 01:22:23.800
lease for the organization of a trading

01:22:23.800 --> 01:22:26.300
network, retail trade, for the

01:22:26.300 --> 01:22:29.080
installation of tents, kiosks have

01:22:29.080 --> 01:22:32.400
been transferred to a single tax

01:22:33.060 --> 01:22:35.260
on the assigned income.

01:22:36.860 --> 01:22:39.200
The reporting period of this tax

01:22:39.200 --> 01:22:41.820
is the first quarter, the first

01:22:41.920 --> 01:22:44.600
half-year, 9 months, and the tax

01:22:44.600 --> 01:22:46.460
period is considered a year.

01:22:47.160 --> 01:22:53.960
With this system, the payment of advance

01:22:53.960 --> 01:22:57.320
payments, which are taken into account when calculating

01:22:57.320 --> 01:23:00.160
the single tax on the end of the year,

01:23:00.160 --> 01:23:02.480
is also introduced.

01:23:02.980 --> 01:23:06.420
The payment period is the 25th of the

01:23:06.420 --> 01:23:08.900
month following the reporting quarter.

01:23:08.920 --> 01:23:10.820
Let us take a small example of calculating

01:23:10.820 --> 01:23:13.720
the tax of an enterprise on a single

01:23:13.720 --> 01:23:16.120
tax on the assigned income.

01:23:16.680 --> 01:23:19.560
Our farm provides household services.

01:23:19.780 --> 01:23:22.580
In the region where our company

01:23:22.580 --> 01:23:25.500
operates, the basic Revenue on household

01:23:25.500 --> 01:23:27.920
services is 7500 rubles

01:23:27.920 --> 01:23:30.040
per month.

01:23:30.600 --> 01:23:32.480
For the calculation of the single

01:23:32.480 --> 01:23:34.020
tax we must take into account

01:23:34.020 --> 01:23:35.700
the number of employees of this enterprise,

01:23:35.700 --> 01:23:37.920
for example, in January 2008

01:23:37.920 --> 01:23:39.940
the number of employees of our

01:23:39.940 --> 01:23:42.140
enterprise was 3 people, in February

01:23:42.240 --> 01:23:45.480
7, and in March already 8 people.

01:23:46.300 --> 01:23:48.500
The tax base for the current

01:23:48.500 --> 01:23:50.140
period, i.e. for the first quarter

01:23:50.140 --> 01:23:53.440
of 2008, will be calculated

01:23:53.440 --> 01:23:54.640
as follows.

01:23:55.040 --> 01:23:57.900
Basic return of 7500 rubles, multiplied

01:23:57.900 --> 01:24:04.900
by the number of employees of the enterprise

01:24:04.900 --> 01:24:07.280
and the adjusting coefficients

01:24:07.280 --> 01:24:10.720
of the basic return established

01:24:10.720 --> 01:24:12.580
in this region, will show that in

01:24:12.580 --> 01:24:16.220
the first quarter of 2008 the enterprise

01:24:16.220 --> 01:24:20.880
will have to pay the effect

01:24:20.880 --> 01:24:26.080
of the application of the ENOVD,

01:24:26.080 --> 01:24:28.860
that is, the single tax on the

01:24:28.860 --> 01:24:30.980
incurred income, is

01:24:32.280 --> 01:24:33.880
quite obvious.

01:24:34.900 --> 01:24:37.720
Because the amount of the single

01:24:37.720 --> 01:24:40.580
tax does not depend on income

01:24:40.580 --> 01:24:42.660
and expenses, it is possible

01:24:42.660 --> 01:24:46.900
to significantly save on wages or

01:24:46.900 --> 01:24:49.460
the number of accounting employees

01:24:49.460 --> 01:24:53.880
involved in the process of registration

01:24:53.880 --> 01:24:55.220
of financial business

01:24:55.220 --> 01:24:59.300
operations of this enterprise.

01:24:59.360 --> 01:25:02.520
Also easily filled in tax declaration,

01:25:02.520 --> 01:25:06.160
which should only indicate the

01:25:06.160 --> 01:25:08.100
amount of the single tax, which

01:25:08.100 --> 01:25:11.200
in the same way as the method of application

01:25:11.200 --> 01:25:19.000
of income in the application of

01:25:19.000 --> 01:25:21.380
the simplified taxation system

