of our program.

01:26:40.280 --> 01:26:42.760
The effectiveness of running your

01:26:42.760 --> 01:26:47.320
business and the duration of

01:26:47.320 --> 01:26:48.920
your company's activities, as you

01:26:48.920 --> 01:26:51.620
already realized, probably depends

01:26:51.620 --> 01:26:55.880
on the correct choice of the tax system.

