The system of taxation, as well as the

01:26:58.460 --> 01:27:00.380
procedure for calculating certain

01:27:00.380 --> 01:27:03.420
taxes and fees, is reflected in the

01:27:03.420 --> 01:27:05.600
accounting policy of the enterprise,

01:27:05.700 --> 01:27:08.560
which is approved literally on

01:27:08.560 --> 01:27:09.520
each enterprise.

01:27:09.560 --> 01:27:10.860
It does not matter what

01:27:10.860 --> 01:27:14.880
tax system this organization operates.

01:27:15.060 --> 01:27:17.360
Therefore, many employees of the

01:27:17.360 --> 01:27:19.860
company, as well as external

01:27:19.860 --> 01:27:22.100
users of the reporting policy,

01:27:22.100 --> 01:27:24.120
must understand.

01:27:24.660 --> 01:27:28.280
These include the head of an organization

01:27:28.280 --> 01:27:31.140
that approves this accounting policy

01:27:31.140 --> 01:27:33.400
