for compliance with the methods

01:27:57.140 --> 01:27:59.800
and techniques, options established

01:27:59.840 --> 01:28:01.700
by the legislation, the financial

01:28:03.080 --> 01:28:05.180
director who is responsible

01:28:05.180 --> 01:28:07.340
for optimizing cash flows and

01:28:07.340 --> 01:28:09.400
