01:28:09.400 --> 01:28:15.300
depending on the volumes

01:28:15.300 --> 01:28:17.920
of tax payments.

01:28:18.860 --> 01:28:21.620
The accounting policy should

01:28:21.620 --> 01:28:23.460
be understood and the tax inspector,

01:28:23.920 --> 01:28:26.540
who considers the accounting policy

01:28:26.540 --> 01:28:29.360
when calculating the tax choices

01:28:29.360 --> 01:28:31.780
