01:28:35.060 --> 01:28:36.640
Thus, when drawing up accounting

01:28:36.640 --> 01:28:39.880
policies, employees of the

01:28:41.340 --> 01:28:44.100
company are interested in successful

01:28:44.100 --> 01:28:48.420
business development.

01:28:49.520 --> 01:28:52.800
If you apply a general tax

01:28:52.800 --> 01:28:55.140
system, the main element

01:28:55.140 --> 01:28:57.960
of tax planning will

01:28:57.960 --> 01:29:01.360
be the income tax.

01:29:01.720 --> 01:29:03.500
It is here that there are many options,

01:29:03.500 --> 01:29:07.460
techniques, recognition and accounting

01:29:07.460 --> 01:29:10.420
of income expenses.

01:29:10.420 --> 01:29:13.000
The main elements of the income

01:29:13.000 --> 01:29:17.780
tax are income and expenses.

01:29:17.780 --> 01:29:19.440
Income under the general system

01:29:19.440 --> 01:29:21.120
of taxation includes, in particular,

01:29:21.120 --> 01:29:23.940
income from the sale of the products

01:29:23.940 --> 01:29:25.740
produced by the company, the

01:29:25.740 --> 01:29:28.540
works performed or the services rendered,

01:29:28.540 --> 01:29:31.620
the property received free of charge

01:29:31.620 --> 01:29:33.940
or the works and services rendered to

01:29:33.940 --> 01:29:37.020
you free of charge, income in the form

01:29:37.180 --> 01:29:39.280
of penalties, which were charged

01:29:39.340 --> 01:29:43.460
in violation of the terms

01:29:43.460 --> 01:29:45.600
of the economic contracts of your

01:29:45.600 --> 01:29:48.000
counterparty, interest in the

01:29:48.520 --> 01:29:52.620
form of interest on the balance

01:29:52.620 --> 01:29:54.460
of funds on your settlement account

01:29:54.460 --> 01:29:58.040
or interest on the other enterprises

01:29:58.040 --> 01:30:00.140
issued by you, in one form

01:30:00.140 --> 01:30:05.020
or another.

01:30:05.020 --> 01:30:10.100
Thus, it is possible to regulate, knowing

01:30:10.100 --> 01:30:16.240
the options for receiving income and the

01:30:16.240 --> 01:30:18.620
order of taxation of these incomes,

01:30:18.740 --> 01:30:21.200
the enterprise can plan the receipt

01:30:21.200 --> 01:30:24.040
of revenue and the outflow of money

01:30:24.040 --> 01:30:28.640
in the form of taxes to the budget.

01:30:29.140 --> 01:30:31.380
The second element of income

01:30:31.380 --> 01:30:34.120
tax planning is expenses.

01:30:34.360 --> 01:30:36.160
In this case, the tax code

01:30:36.160 --> 01:30:39.560
presents a very wide range of options.

01:30:40.540 --> 01:30:42.120
For example, if you rent a

01:30:42.120 --> 01:30:45.280
room, then the costs in the

01:30:45.280 --> 01:30:48.780
form of rent can be taken into account

01:30:48.780 --> 01:30:51.800
in the tax base when calculating

01:30:51.800 --> 01:30:59.020
one of the three options.

01:30:59.080 --> 01:31:01.100
The first option is on the date of

01:31:01.100 --> 01:31:03.700
submission of documents to you from

01:31:03.700 --> 01:31:05.880
the tenant, the second option is on the

01:31:05.880 --> 01:31:07.960
last day of the reporting period and the

01:31:07.960 --> 01:31:11.340
third option is on the date of settlements

01:31:11.340 --> 01:31:14.580
with the tenant.

01:31:14.580 --> 01:31:20.180
If you know that you will not be

01:31:20.180 --> 01:31:22.600
a regular payer of rent, it is desirable

01:31:22.600 --> 01:31:27.780
to save tax payments when calculating

01:31:27.780 --> 01:31:30.100
the method to choose the method

01:31:30.100 --> 01:31:33.560
of recognition of income in

01:31:33.560 --> 01:31:38.080
the form of rent on the date

01:31:38.080 --> 01:31:41.760
of presentation to you documents.

01:31:44.000 --> 01:31:46.880
The next important and

01:31:46.880 --> 01:31:49.620
most common point of

01:31:49.620 --> 01:31:51.940
tax planning is tax planning

01:31:51.940 --> 01:31:56.580
with the application of the

01:31:56.580 --> 01:31:58.780
simplified tax system.

01:31:59.160 --> 01:32:00.380
As we have already considered

01:32:00.380 --> 01:32:04.600
before, the main element and choice

01:32:04.600 --> 01:32:09.080
of your business should be planning

01:32:09.080 --> 01:32:11.860
your income and expenses, calculating

01:32:11.860 --> 01:32:14.560
profitability, which affects the

01:32:14.660 --> 01:32:17.120
choice of the object of taxation

01:32:17.120 --> 01:32:19.360
under this system and which

01:32:19.360 --> 01:32:21.100
you are not entitled to change

01:32:21.100 --> 01:32:23.760
during the tax period.

