In other words, if you have submitted

01:32:27.160 --> 01:32:29.820
a statement to the tax inspectorate

01:32:29.820 --> 01:32:31.700
before November 30 that you wish to

01:32:31.700 --> 01:32:35.120
calculate income, for example,

01:32:35.120 --> 01:32:38.700
by the method of income minus expenses,

01:32:38.700 --> 01:32:43.400
you are entitled to change your choice

01:32:43.400 --> 01:32:45.700
only within 20 days, that is, only

01:32:45.700 --> 01:32:49.700
until December 20 of this year, preceding

01:32:49.700 --> 01:32:51.440
the application of the simplified

01:32:51.440 --> 01:32:54.380
taxation system, and during

01:32:54.380 --> 01:32:57.080
the year of application of the

01:32:57.080 --> 01:32:59.940
simplified system you are

01:32:59.940 --> 01:33:05.260
not entitled to make any adjustments.

01:33:05.900 --> 01:33:09.080
You, based on the choice of

01:33:09.080 --> 01:33:10.780
the object of taxation in the

01:33:10.780 --> 01:33:13.400
simplified taxation system, should

01:33:13.400 --> 01:33:16.580
make your contracts, not

01:33:16.580 --> 01:33:20.140
sales, but intermediary, to

01:33:20.140 --> 01:33:22.380
organize the documents of turnover

01:33:22.380 --> 01:33:23.720
accordingly.

01:33:24.180 --> 01:33:28.380
If you chose the object

01:33:28.380 --> 01:33:31.040
of taxation "Income", then for you,

01:33:31.040 --> 01:33:33.900
the documents related to expenses

01:33:33.900 --> 01:33:36.340
will not be as important as when

01:33:36.340 --> 01:33:39.120
choosing another option, which

01:33:39.160 --> 01:33:40.900
works with the simplified

01:33:40.900 --> 01:33:42.420
taxation system.

01:33:43.540 --> 01:33:48.060
Due to the fact that with the income method

01:33:48.060 --> 01:33:49.220
on the simplified system

01:33:49.380 --> 01:33:51.840
of taxation the amount of the single

01:33:51.840 --> 01:33:54.040
tax you have the right to reduce the

01:33:54.040 --> 01:33:56.380
accrual to the Pension Fund of

01:33:56.380 --> 01:33:58.280
the Russian Federation on

01:33:58.280 --> 01:33:59.740
the accrual payments to your

